c6d3f15c6c20ab51.png&h=b0f19962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/050848_2adc30944c822ff028bad2dfafed2681.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F050848_2adc30944c822ff028bad2dfafed2681.png&h=3a777140&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/050851_2b682c3c23edd53d55e77a5bb56ede23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F050851_2b682c3c23edd53d55e77a5bb56ede23.png&h=ae70827c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"575e9ed1dbb8daa1628d502fb62c535976594dc9","tid":825652,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"啤酒節正唔正"},{"pid":"977fdf6d3acf535a080cdc366b45aeaae875d395","tid":825652,"uid":126221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"啤酒節 d 住宿貴到傻，可以留意一下 AirBnB，當年去既時候連 AirBnB 都爆爆地。<br />\n<br />\n你話當地人對遊客好惡，基本上唔覺，全程英語 (無人識德文) 基本上無見過有人面黑。<br />\n<br />\n入夜前去 d 帳幕到食野，守規距基本上無人理你係本地定外國人，<br />\n因為真係收得唔平 (樣樣都差唔多 10 歐起跳)，加埋小費，基本上佢地都係希望多 d 人去。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨是見過一次面黑係當我拎住 Jar 檸檬汁同人乾杯時，對面就真係黑住面咁同我講 ...<br />\nProst 乜春，你呢 Jar 檸檬汁 黎喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，有機會要去試下 Paulaner 個帳幕，第一次飲佢既生啤，<br />\n簡真係驚為天人，原來生啤可以咁好味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b425e8b5a248734f1c2d961f102bc6258548ccf3","tid":825652,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"好想去 但住宿好貴 又冇人share"},{"pid":"0eee14705d5352310359882e1b54225cfc844625","tid":825652,"uid":81165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"977fdf6d3acf535a080cdc366b45aeaae875d395","tid":825652,"uid":126221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"啤酒節 d 住宿貴到傻，可以留意一下 AirBnB，當年去既時候連 AirBnB 都爆爆地。<br />\n<br />\n你話當地人對遊客好惡，基本上唔覺，全程英語